'''CenturyTel of Redfield, Inc.''' is a telephone operating of [[CenturyLink]] providing local telephone services to [[Redfield, Arkansas]]. The company was founded in 1970. It is one of several CenturyLink companies providing telephone service in [[Arkansas]].
